attributes.description:
Peugeot 2008 1.2T Allure Auto sits well on its wheels, perfectly shouldered, strong, and reassuring.
Safety Features
Full LED headlights with Smartbeam Assist;
LED daytime running lights with distinctive ‘Tooth’ design;
ABS with EBD and EBA (Emergency Braking Assistance);
Airbags: Driver and front passenger airbags;
Alarm (Thatcham approved)
